{"about_the_game":"Platypus is a fast, frantic and fun arcade-style shoot-em-up!!<br><br>The vast continent-spanning city of Collosatropolis has finally reached the limits of its expansion. Tall buildings cover every available space. The air is thick with smoke and poisonous chemicals. Parking is a nightmare.<br><br>The Collosotropolan leaders have decided the simplest solution is to invade the neighbouring country of Mungola. They don't anticipate much of a struggle - Mungolans are simple, earthy types without much love for industry. In fact, Mungola's entire defence force consists of a single squadron of fighter planes - the venerable F-27 &quot;Platypus&quot;.<br><br>What possible threat could a few antique aircraft be to the mighty Collosotropolan Battle Fleet...?<br><br>To the Mungolan people the venerable F-27 &quot;Platypus&quot; is their last best hope for freedom!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Unlimited Play<br></li><li>Two-Player Simultaneous Action<br></li><li>Stunning Claymation Graphics<br></li><li>Addictive, Exciting Game Play<br></li><li>Adjustable Difficulty Settings<br></li><li>Perfect for the Entire Family</li></ul>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/307340?t=1595797105","background_raw":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/307340?t=1595797105","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/307340/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1595797105","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/307340/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1595797105","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"Shared/Split Screen","id":24},{"description":"Steam Trading Cards","id":29},{"description":"Remote Play Together","id":44},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<h1>Exclusive News!</h1><p>Platypus creator, Anthony Flack, has got the license back for Platypus!<br><br>We've put together a small team, Claymatic Games, and are doing more stop-motion games. Our first is an all action brawler for 1 to 8 players called Clodhoppers. We'll also be doing a remastered version of Platypus!<br><br>We have a friendly, active Platypus community on the claymatic.games Discord - please join us :)</p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>Platypus is a fast, frantic and fun arcade-style shoot-em-up!!<br><br>The vast continent-spanning city of Collosatropolis has finally reached the limits of its expansion. Tall buildings cover every available space. The air is thick with smoke and poisonous chemicals. Parking is a nightmare.<br><br>The Collosotropolan leaders have decided the simplest solution is to invade the neighbouring country of Mungola. They don't anticipate much of a struggle - Mungolans are simple, earthy types without much love for industry. In fact, Mungola's entire defence force consists of a single squadron of fighter planes - the venerable F-27 &quot;Platypus&quot;.<br><br>What possible threat could a few antique aircraft be to the mighty Collosotropolan Battle Fleet...?<br><br>To the Mungolan people the venerable F-27 &quot;Platypus&quot; is their last best hope for freedom!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Unlimited Play<br></li><li>Two-Player Simultaneous Action<br></li><li>Stunning Claymation Graphics<br></li><li>Addictive, Exciting Game Play<br></li><li>Adjustable Difficulty Settings<br></li><li>Perfect for the Entire Family</li></ul>","developers":["Anthony Flack"],"genres":[{"description":"Action","id":"1"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/307340/header.jpg?t=1595797105","is_free":false,"linux_requirements":[],"mac_requirements":[],"movies":[{"highlight":true,"id":2033969,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/2033969/movie480.mp4?t=1447363224","max"